The Southern African Venture Capital and Private Equity Association’s (Savca), 2017 Venture Capital (VC) Success Stories report highlights the role that VC plays in supporting South African business, and follows the launch of the Savca 2017 VC Survey that revealed that VC investments in ICT comprised 27% of the deals concluded in 2016.
